languages.text: "Подумай сам — хоть кому-то Последний восход сделал лучше? Одни умирают, другим выжигают глаза, третьи сходят с ума".

traits.locale_text: "Подумай сам — хоть кому-то Последний Восход сделал лучше? Одни умирают, другим выжигают глаза, третьи сходят с ума".

languages.text: "Think about it. What good has the Final Dawn done for anyone at all? Some have died. Some have had their eyes burnt out. Some have gone insane."

languages.text: "Denkt doch einmal nach. Was hat die Letzte Dämmerung je Gutes für irgendjemanden bewirkt? Manche sind gestorben. Manchen wurden die Augen ausgebrannt. Manche sind wahnsinnig geworden."

languages.text: « Réfléchissez. L'Aube finale s'est-elle déjà montrée bienveillante envers qui que ce soit ? Des gens sont morts. D'autres ont eu les yeux brûlés. Certains sont devenus fous. »
languages.original_text: "Think about it. What good has the Final Dawn done for anyone at all? Some have died. Some have had their eyes burnt out. Some have gone insane."

languages.text: “好好想想，终末黎明到底给人们带来了什么好处？一部分人死了，一部分人的眼睛被烧掉了，还有的人发疯了。”
languages.original_text: "Think about it. What good has the Final Dawn done for anyone at all? Some have died. Some have had their eyes burnt out. Some have gone insane."

traits.locale_text: “好好想想，终末黎明到底给人们带来了什么好处？一部分人死了，一部分人的眼睛被烧掉了，还有的人发疯了。”

languages.text: 「考えてみるんだ。最後の夜明けは、いったい誰に何の役に立ったと言うのだ？死んだ者もいる。また、ある者は目を焼かれた。何人かは狂気に陥った」
languages.original_text: "Think about it. What good has the Final Dawn done for anyone at all? Some have died. Some have had their eyes burnt out. Some have gone insane."

languages.text: «Piénselo. ¿De qué ha servido el Amanecer Final? Algunos han muerto. A algunos les han quemado los ojos. Algunos se han vuelto locos».

languages.text: "Bir düşün. Nihai Şafak'ın kime faydası dokundu? Ölenler oldu. Gözleri dağlananlar, delirenler oldu."
